# House Price Prediction using Linear Regression

## Overview

This repository contains a solution to predict house prices based on the house's square footage, number of bedrooms, and number of bathrooms using a linear regression model. The model is trained and evaluated on the Ames Housing dataset, a common dataset used for regression tasks.

